abstract: Republicans in Nevada are caucusing Saturday. We'll be bringing you occasional updates.
lead_paragraph: Republicans in Nevada are caucusing today. The state's Republican party will begin to report results after 5 p.m., but final numbers will take several more hours. On the other hand, unofficial results are already being reported from some precincts. Throughout, we'll bring you occasional updates.
